{"tid":51053,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣(3)","createTime":"2016-12-23T01:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T10:19:41.000Z","uid":38437,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05fb6878a8401f1dd88a91558204e46dcc405148","tid":51053,"uid":38437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:57:01.000Z","msg":"見無人開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自己試下開"},{"pid":"c6401061bf27bdde9529f17affc7dee5fa4d8fdb","tid":51053,"uid":38437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:57:33.000Z","msg":"秋季新劇: 《逃避雖可恥但有用》 <br />\n官網: <a href=\"http://www.tbs.co.jp/NIGEHAJI_tbs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tbs.co.jp%2FNIGEHAJI_tbs%2F&d=aQNfnfxYN1hGCgQEnulAvWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=0e7bc447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.tbs.co.jp/NIGEHAJI_tbs/</a> FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nigehaji.tbs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnigehaji.tbs%2F&d=aQNfnfxYN1hGCgQEnulAvWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=9435084a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nigehaji.tbs/</a> Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/nigehaji_tbs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnigehaji_tbs%2F&d=aQNfnfxYN1hGCgQEnulAvWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=bc95df6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nigehaji_tbs/</a> Instagram id: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/nigehajigram/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fnigehajigram%2F&d=aQNfnfxYN1hGCgQEnulAvWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=2e8fd365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/nigehajigram/</a> 預告片: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nM2MAx6_65Y&amp;amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnM2MAx6_65Y%26amp%3Bfeature%3Dyoutu.be%26amp%3Bfeature%3Dyoutu.be&d=aQNfnfxYN1hGCgQEnulAvWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=a8f81d63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nM2MAx6_65Y&amp;amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n出演:新垣結衣/星野源/大谷亮平/藤井隆/真野&amp;amp;#24693;里菜/成田凌/山賀琴子/宇&amp;amp;#26806;剛士/富田靖子/古田新太/石田百和子 <br />\n<br />\n主題曲: 星野 源 - &amp;amp;#24651; <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jhOVibLEDhA&amp;amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjhOVibLEDhA%26amp%3Bfeature%3Dyoutu.be%26amp%3Bfeature%3Dyoutu.be&d=aQNfnfxYN1hGCgQEnulAvWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=d83e61d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jhOVibLEDhA&amp;amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n&amp;amp;#24651;&amp;amp;#12480;&amp;amp;#12531;&amp;amp;#12473;教學片: <a href=\"http://youtu.be/MOyGxzG91yo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMOyGxzG91yo&d=aQNfnfxYN1hGCgQEnulAvWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=9283581e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/MOyGxzG91yo</a><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女星新垣結衣接拍十月開播TBS日劇《逃避雖可恥但有用》，飾演像上班一樣為特定目的結婚的新妻，劇集根據海野津波在月刊《Kiss》連載的同名漫畫改編，以&ldquo;丈夫是雇主，妻子是職員&rdquo;的價值觀為基礎，講述契約結婚的主人公的故事。<br />\n<br />\n　　劇中新垣結衣飾演主人公森山，這位25歲愛妄想的女子沒有男友，畢業後沒有工作，做派遣職員沒公司用，生活不順終日煩惱，她幫單身職員津崎做家務，對方提出不如像上班一樣結婚，於是他們秘密定下契約，開始了&ldquo;丈夫是雇主，妻子是職員&rdquo;的新婚生活。<br />\n<br />\n　　原作者海野津波說：&ldquo;還沒確定日劇化的時候，我就和朋友們幻想過真人版的演員，當時還說如果讓新垣結衣演森山怎麼樣，如果她主演的話絕對能拿滿分，聽說日劇版真的是新垣結衣主演我特別開心。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　制作人那須田淳說：&ldquo;剛讀原著的時候，主人公契約結婚和新婚愛情生活之間巧妙的關聯讓我感覺很有趣，主題非常能引起現代人的共鳴。我認為有幽默感又有表現力的新垣結衣是這個角色的最佳人選，一定能把歡笑和勇氣傳達給觀眾。&rdquo;制作人宮崎真佐子說：&ldquo;因為契約結婚而一起生活的兩位主人公的關系很有趣，觀眾應該比較容易帶入感情，工作和結婚是現在很重要的社會問題。也許很多人都有誰真的需要自己這樣的煩惱，劇中會有詳細的描寫。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"e4c64bddce52a8a4bd4c91e071871bab413e94b6","tid":51053,"uid":38437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:58:34.000Z","msg":"FAIL"},{"pid":"94bcaa7dc96a7b3e027f8ea4b052234025993831","tid":51053,"uid":50334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T02:17:06.000Z","msg":"重開定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12951bd85c23fc04bf19d6a6d18591806821b05","tid":51053,"uid":38437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T02:18:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重開定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無所謂 你可以開 唔識搞FORMAT"},{"pid":"0db65bf6a0b25ec80c297de3b8ca9ec3740b8b47","tid":51053,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:22:49.000Z","msg":"結衣其實眼細細， <br />\n帶咗大眼仔靚好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n逃避呢套 成套片真係靠結衣。。<br />\n劇情真係一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  FF 撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e44a827e340f8a7ac835e3a0601852cc7d28be","tid":51053,"uid":2914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T10:19:41.000Z","msg":"你地有冇買年暦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}